creator: Tap Story
descriptionHtml:
🍭Sweet Crush Royal is a new and cute candy & cake match-3 game. Brand new visual effect and game experience. Cakes, bread, candies and juicy jelly, lots of desserts open your taste palate feast while playing.
🍬The candy crush process is fun and easy. You can collect delicious candies and delicious cakes in the game, as well as some unexpected surprises.

👑【How to play】
- Swipe and match 3 candies of the same color to blast and win points!
- Match 4 and more candies to create a magic candy bomb！
- Use tasty and powerful boosters candy to crush the Ice layer, virus and bread!
- Any two candy boosters can be combined into a more powerful explosion effect！

🍰【Game Features】
-Thousands of juicy puzzle levels full of candies and 6000+ levels！
- Well-designed in sweet graphics & interface！
- Relaxing background music & Amazing animations！
- Free game that can play any time and anywhere!

💖Download now and start your candy adventure!💖
